bib_record.title: Determination of 29Si level density from 3 to 22 MeV

free_txt: Corrected for charged-particle escape from within the
Si surface barrier detector served as both
target and detector flux monitored using CH2 radiator.
Energy resolution 8 keV at 5 MeV to 40 keV at 13 MeV
